OL,3,CFamily of Ann Widdecombe announce
OL,4,Cpublic memorial
OL,6,FJoshua Kerry, 28, from Rotherham,
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire, appeared in court on
OL,8,FTuesday charged with her murder.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Widdecombe's family
OL,11,Fsaid arrangements for a private
OL,12,Ffuneral service for her family and
OL,13,Fclose friends had already been made.
OL,15,F"A private service for family and
OL,16,Fclose friends will be held in the
OL,17,Fcoming weeks, and invitations for this
OL,18,Fceremony have been distributed," they
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
