OL,3,CFamily of Ann Widdecombe announce
OL,4,Cpublic memorial
OL,6,F"A more public memorial will follow
OL,7,Flater in the year, the details of
OL,8,Fwhich will be released in due course.
OL,10,F"While we are very grateful for the
OL,11,Fwide expression of condolences, the
OL,12,Ffamily would ask that this initial
OL,13,Fservice is limited to those closest to
OL,14,FAnn."
OL,16,FWiddecombe had been eating lunch when
OL,17,FKerry allegedly pulled up outside the
OL,18,Ffront of her bungalow in a red
OL,19,FVauxhall Corsa and entered through the
OL,20,Ffront door, prosecutors said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@EO]
