OL,3,CFamily of Ann Widdecombe announce
OL,4,Cpublic memorial
OL,6,FWiddecombe was first elected as a
OL,7,FConservative MP in Kent in 1987, was a
OL,8,Fprisons minister in the 1990s and
OL,9,Flater became an MEP for the Brexit
OL,10,FParty.
OL,12,FAt the time of her death she was a
OL,13,Fspokeswoman on immigration and justice
OL,14,Ffor Reform UK.
OL,16,FShe also found fame outside politics
OL,17,Fon Strictly Come Dancing and Celebrity
OL,18,FBig Brother.
